    "As shown in Figure 3, we retrieved 2,970 publications from all three databases.",
    "We used the Zotero reference management tool to automatically detect duplicates, which we manually double-checked.",
    "We discarded 545 duplicates: 517 were identified by Zotero, and 28 by manual inspection.",
    "Screening discarding 1,687 publications and retaining 738 publications for further analysis.",
    "Afterwards, we conducted an intermediate screening step based on the venue quality."
